      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SURREALIST (1) is an honest type rarely out of the money, scoring at Capalaba (19.74) last time and making it two straight wins. Form at the trip excellent including five wins. Rates strongly and will go close from the inside draw. RITZA KEN (5) racing well without winning, placing at his last five runs. Last start finished 2nd over 550m at Q Lakeside beaten 2 lengths (30.87) behind Tripper Art in a Grade 4/5 on March 28. Didn't win last time but still ran one of the quickest times on the card. Racing well and deserves a win. SILVER MOON (2) missed the frame latest (38.30) when seventh over 600m at this track in a Restricted WIN. Has already won out of this draw. Looks suited here and can measure up.",
